---
title: Creamy Shrimp Linguine with Crunchy Parmesan Topping
description: All the elements in this dish are classics that are made for one another. Shrimp, spinach and tarragon have nothing but love for one another and couldn't pair better with a creamy sauce and pasta. Enjoy!
